name: || Russ || #001
description: This is Russ. Russ lives downtown in Erie, PA. He asked me for a dollar the other day. I told him that I would trade him for a photograph and that if I made any money from it, I would find him and split it with him. Russ definitely doesn't think I'm comin back... The first $100 is for Russ. The next $100 I will keep for expenses. The rest will go to a local charity/mission/center of my choice.
